Message
About the job
We are working with a high-performance, global trading and technology firm seeking a Software Engineer to join their engineering team in New York.


Key Responsibilities

Design & deploy software that supports trading activities and business functions
Collaborate with business stakeholders to define priorities and deliver custom technology solutions
Analyze complex business and technical problems, and take proactive, self-directed action to solve them
Provide timely systems support for live trading/production environments


Required Skills & Experience

Deep proficiency in Python and a strong passion for software development
Professional exposure to distributed systems
Good knowledge of software development life-cycle (SDLC) methodologies
Excellent communication and interpersonal skill
Minimum Bachelor’s degree in Computer Science or a related field


Preferred / Bonus Qualifications

Experience with trading systems
Familiarity with machine learning/statistical methods
Experience with C++, SQL, kdb or similar technologies


Total comp: base up to 250k, tc into the 7 figures
